item.title: CVE-2022-34453|2024-08-03T09:15:15.129Z -- dell -- xtremio%20x2
item.description: Dell XtremIO X2 XMS versions prior to 6-4-1.11 contain an improper access control vulnerability. A remote read only user could potentially exploit this vulnerability to perform add/delete QoS policies which are disabled by default.
